DOC.brief_summary: Dill is herbaceous and aromatic herb used in order to convenient and shorter labor in Iran. The objective of this study was to evaluate the effect of Dill seed on uterus contractions in active phase of labor.
DOC.brief_title: Effect of Dill Seed on Uterus Contractions Pattern
DOC.criteria: 1835 yrs, primiparous, having single fetus with cephalic presentation, gestational age 3742 weeks, having no medical diseases, having no history of hospitalization due to psychological diseases, having no addiction to cigarette, having no complications during pregnancy such as hypertension, and BMI< 26.
